parcel.name: Null Gallery
parcel.description:
Welcome to the gallery at the center of the world. This parcel is built to represent the voxels head quarters in Wellington New Zealand.

Nau mai ki te whare toi i te pokapū o te ao. Kua hangaia tēnei poraka hei tohu i te tari matua o voxels ki Wellington, Aotearoa.
